data: {"type":"result","content":"aking varies across studies, techniques, and genetic subgroups. Additionally, the prognostic signifi"}

data: {"type":"result","content":"cance of MRD may differ based on the specific immunophenotypic or molecular marker being tracked. In"}

data: {"type":"result","content":"tegration of MRD assessment with other risk factors remains an area of active investigation, as does"}

